    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="How can I use the Shoutout function?" class="article-title">
          How can I use the Shoutout function?
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p><span>When starting their live broadcast, the distributor can choose to activate the Shoutout function.<br><br>Distributors need to agree to the "Rewards Reception Terms of Use" in order to be able to receive rewards from pixiv. (*For more information about Rewards, <a href="https://sketch.pixiv.help/hc/en/sections/360001459834">click here</a>.)<br><br>Viewers can send shoutouts (emoji) to a distributor by consuming pixiv Points. (<a href="https://sketch.pixiv.help/hc/en/sections/360001134914">Click here</a> for detailed information on pixiv Points.) </span></p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

